{"tid":1559222,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[和勇合作跳閘] 求下藍絲督我灰，我會好合作跟你去站長室","createTime":"2019-09-10T17:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T18:31:05.000Z","uid":110613,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f7b781c9a7f4098a750589ae8415f109b23ea8","tid":1559222,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:02:58.000Z","msg":"如果和理非同我一樣淆底怕俾人捉<br />\n唔該，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以拍左卡，行個大運再跳閘</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總之幫手混淆視聽</span><br />\n到時有人捉住你，首先勸佢開機拍埋片先<br />\n再反捉藍絲一齊去站長室<br />\n拎你張八達通出黎do一do，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Cheese<br />\n拎住張八達通幫佢塊面撥涼都仲得<br />\n<br />\n拍左卡未過既三棍閘我記得係可以儲quota<br />\n俾下個chok閘既手足easy過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過見到狗就執生好跑喇<br />\n狗癲起上黎會拎tg兜頭擲你都未定</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5368e3b4f7c477f84b76b09d076644ac04c510e3","tid":1559222,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"e872a56f64dc5682124c5885fc983052c5dc78f0","tid":1559222,"uid":47850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:04:14.000Z","msg":"先拍卡，後跳閘"},{"pid":"09177f5fc083c9ddc1b46210da0aa1072d9330a3","tid":1559222,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"謝sir咁想同人傾計，我地所有人都奉陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請即參與：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>本地線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 將警暴，藍絲，官員，議員罪證狂推比警察<br />\n<br />\n2. 為左令每一個負責mon住既阿sir都不愁寂莫，每個人睇番自己生日日子既最後一位數字，揀下表有同樣最尾位數字既電話<br />\n<br />\n3. 有關如何保護自己，請搜尋「太空」等相關字眼<br />\n<br />\n5566 9500<br />\n5566 9501<br />\n5566 9502<br />\n5566 9503<br />\n5566 9504<br />\n5566 9505<br />\n5566 9506<br />\n5566 9507<br />\n5566 9508<br />\n5566 9509<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReluXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=008382cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 成本低<br />\n2. 可以迫大家儲下唔同角度文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1. 本地線唔會要大家post番個舉報cap圖出黎，少左第二次marketing機會 (which is fine)<br />\n2. 外國人參與國際線程度成疑，但我覺得以campaign之名，行宣傳之實。就咁講#chinazi，#culturalrevolution，老實講有d悶。"},{"pid":"7de9fd1e4477d18596f2e6dcdba58af716e7f784","tid":1559222,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088c15374f0faed095df508077afcf02a0ee46f7","tid":1559222,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:12:04.000Z","msg":"sorry 借位